INTELLECTUAL PROPERTY NOTICE
-----------------------------
The Multi-Agent Debate System, including but not limited to:

  - The multi-mode debate orchestration architecture (same-model,
    cross-model, and human-vs-AI debate modes)
  - The real-time LLM token streaming pipeline with server-side
    text-to-speech integration
  - The LangGraph-based multi-agent state graph design with per-agent
    LLM routing, human-in-the-loop pause/resume, and live moderation
